cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about computer vision and machine learning techniques for multi-person 2D pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of nonparametric representation and refinement techniques, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of hand and facial keypoints, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the real-time performance of the proposed method, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO).
